  <section class="app-c-header-notice" aria-label="notice" role="region">
    <div class="app-c-header-notice__header">
      <h2 class="app-c-header-notice__title">New rules for January 2021</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="app-c-header-notice__content">
          <p class="app-c-header-notice__text govuk-body">The UK has left the EU, and the transition period after Brexit comes to an end this year.</p>
          <p class="app-c-header-notice__text govuk-body">This page tells you what you'll need to do from 1 January 2021. It will be updated if anything changes.</p>

        <p class="app-c-header-notice__text govuk-body">Check what else you need to do during <a data-module="track-click" data-track-category="no_deal_notice" data-track-action="/transition" data-track-label="the transition period" class="govuk-link" href="/transition">the transition period</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>


<div class="govuk-grid-row">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    

